import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-icons', templateUrl: './icons.component.html', styleUrls: ['./icons.component.css'] }) export class IconsComponent implements OnInit { constructor() { } ngOnInit() { } }

Material Design Icons

Handcrafted by our friends from Google

The icons are visible on Desktop mode inside an iframe. Since the iframe is not working on Mobile and Tablets please visit the icons on their original page on Google. Check the Material Icons
